name: Cute Cat (Free)
description:
The character of the game is a cat which can run, turn and jump in order to move and eats mouse and chick. The more mouse and chick you eat the more score you earn but if you collide with dogs and roosters during game level more than specified times the cat will lose it's health and your score will be added to the table.

Cat health can be upgraded via shop in the game.

You can also buy meat for cat to fill her health bar in the game.
